Use this endpoint to create a repeating section field.
create other fields like short text field, or any of the other valid fields, and then add the slug in the column field.

valid fields:
BOOLEAN,
SHORT_TEXT,
NUMBER,
LONG_TEXT,
EMAIL,
PHONE,
DATE,
TIME,
CITY,
REGEX,
WEBSITE

example:
{
    "type": "repeating_section",
    "title": "test title",
    "column_groups": [
        {"title": "test group 1", "column_field": field_slug},


    ]
}
